page.name: Ancient Frost Moglin Mace IX
page.description: A lost weapon forged by the ancient Frost Moglins, and gifted to you by Papa Moglin as thanks for defeating the legendary wyrm Frallmar! This weapon has a chance to reduce the amount of health your foe can recover. This item requires a Dragon Amulet.
